\begin_layout Standard
Interesting – unlike raw lists,
 vectors come with a robust set of built in operations,
 like headOption,
 drop(),
 lastOption,
 dropRight,
 etc.
 Like we said,
 worth looking into!
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Our next method will be the index method,
